snippet: Winless Connecticut is changing quarterbacks again. Coach T. J. Weist said a redshirt freshman, Casey Cochran, would start on Saturday at Southern Methodist.
abstract: Connecitcut football team, still winless, will try yet another quarterback, replacing Tim Boyle with freshman Casey Cochran.
lead_paragraph: Winless Connecticut is changing quarterbacks again. Coach T. J. Weist said a redshirt freshman, Casey Cochran, would start on Saturday at Southern Methodist.
